reviewText: Low budget movie, as is the whole Shadowchaser series.  Saw this one long ago and have the other two, so figured I'd pick it up. If you are inclined to like these "B" straight to video movies its OK.  If looking for great sci-fi you should skip it.

just childhood memories there. B class. this is supposed to be the 3rd movie of the series, but i never saw the first 2. took me years to remember this movie and by chance i came across a trailer and i looked for the movie.
